5_Comments: I like the approach of combining chest CT scans with patient clinical data/patient information and train an AI system to get more accurate, faster diagnostic. Also like the fact that even through trained on a small sample, the AI can detect COVID where trained radiologists could not. Also like the fact that this could be deployed fast to hospitals around the world. Not clear on API/integration needs with other hospital native data sets.
